on my own.

331
00:31:15.610 --> 00:31:17.077
But in time...

332
00:31:19.480 --> 00:31:23.917
Emilia grew into
a proper English lady.

333
00:31:26.487 --> 00:31:28.489
[eerie music playing]

334
00:31:39.500 --> 00:31:43.036
That's Arthur and Emilia
on their wedding day.

335
00:31:46.039 --> 00:31:48.142
