on behalf of the British Crown.

443
00:44:35.476 --> 00:44:36.710
So...

444
00:44:37.811 --> 00:44:40.447
I'm ordering every one of you

445
00:44:40.549 --> 00:44:42.383
to raise your glasses

446
00:44:43.817 --> 00:44:48.322
