447
00:44:48.422 --> 00:44:52.426
<i>-Kia ora.</i> Cookie! [laughing]
-[all laughing]

448
00:45:00.669 --> 00:45:01.969
But this evening...

449
00:45:03.605 --> 00:45:06.473
